# Exception: everything under docs/ is canonical documentation and must be
# version-controlled. (The blanket *.md ignore above is meant to drop scratch
# notes at the repo root, not the docs/ directory — a per-file exception list
# silently dropped new docs, so allow the whole folder.)
!docs/
!docs/**/*.md